data.title: Exclusive: Is Kamal Haasan contesting from Coimbatore Constituency on his debut?
meta_keywords: Exclusive: Is Kamal Haasan contesting from Coimbatore Constituency on his debut? - simplicity
data.meta_description: Makkal Needhi Maiam which was founded a little over a year ago has taken the plunge to contest in the Lok Sabha Elections in 2019. The party released it’s first set of candidates who are contesting in 21 constituencies yesterday (March 20, 2019).
